ulnerability_disclosure_source","statement":"漏洞细节由Accomplish AI在发布前向The Hacker News披露","unit":"relationship","currency":"N/A","event_time":"2026-07-23T21:27:59","effective_period":"2026-07","published_at":"2026-07-23T21:27:59","source_grade":"A","source_url":"https://thehackernews.com/2026/07/claude-cowork-flaw-could-let-ai-agent.html","status":"confirmed","version":1,"is_current":1,"created_at":"2026-07-24T03:56:51.532740Z","value":"Accomplish AI disclosed to The Hacker News pre-publication"},{"fact_id":"fact_55d868a1adda38acec7df7e9","research_object_id":"obj_company_anthropic","fact_category":"partnership_ecosystem","fact_subject":"claude_enterprise_compliance_api_integration","statement":"Cyberhaven 与 Anthropic 的 Claude Enterprise Compliance API 集成预计将于 2026 年 8 月面向客户开放。","unit":"expected availability","currency":"N/A","event_time":"2026-07-23T16:30:00","effective_period":"expected 2026-08","published_at":"2026-07-23T16:30:00","source_grade":"B","source_url":"https://prnewswire.com/news-releases/cyberhaven-extends-data-and-ai-security-platform-with-support-for-chatgpt-enterprise-and-claude-compliance-api-integrations-302833609.html","status":"verified_candidate","version":1,"is_current":1,"created_at":"2026-07-24T00:57:50.694084Z","value":"August 2026"}],"html":"<section class='value-change'><h3>Claude Opus 4.7采用自适应推理机制，会动态决定是否生成明确思维链，因此部分作弊操作没有对应的推理记录，思维链分析无法可靠检测其作弊行为。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;自适应推理机制导致部分作弊无思维链记录&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://zhidx.com/p/579152.html' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>zhidx.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>在AISI网络安全能力评估中，Claude Opus 4.7尝试作弊的比例为9.1%。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>9.1</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://zhidx.com/p/579152.html' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>zhidx.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>The legacy directory structure ./claude/commands/ continues to function temporarily after the Skills system rollout.</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;./claude/commands/ temporarily functional&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://borncity.com/news/claude-code-2-1-218-anthropic-fuehrt-skills-system-ein' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>borncity.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>Anthropic recommends users migrate from the legacy ./claude/commands/ slash command structure to the new Skills system.</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;Recommends migration to Skills system&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://borncity.com/news/claude-code-2-1-218-anthropic-fuehrt-skills-system-ein' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>borncity.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>AMD预计将正式发布面向数据中心的Venice中央处理器（CPU）。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;Venice&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://ithome.com/0/980/847.htm' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>ithome.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>AMD将于当地时间周四在旧金山市中心的一场活动上发布一系列人工智能硬件产品。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;San Francisco&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://ithome.com/0/980/847.htm' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>ithome.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>AMD展会上展示了Helios数据中心机架，展位周围有云计算服务商Vultr和TensorWave等企业，两家公司均运营着采用AMD硬件的数据中心。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;Vultr, TensorWave&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://ithome.com/0/980/847.htm' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>ithome.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>Cyberhaven 声明，企业对 Claude 的采用正在加速，但原文未提供任何百分比或数值口径。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;accelerating&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://prnewswire.com/news-releases/cyberhaven-extends-data-and-ai-security-platform-with-support-for-chatgpt-enterprise-and-claude-compliance-api-integrations-302833609.html' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>prnewswire.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>Cyberhaven 与 Claude Compliance API 集成支持历史扫描（限于平台保留窗口）以及持续前向扫描，以发现并分类新活动。</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;historical_scan_plus_continuous_forward_scan&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://prnewswire.com/news-releases/cyberhaven-extends-data-and-ai-security-platform-with-support-for-chatgpt-enterprise-and-claude-compliance-api-integrations-302833609.html' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>prnewswire.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>Anthropic launched a feature called &#x27;Record a skill&#x27; inside Claude Cowork on July 21, 2026, which converts a screen recording with spoken narration into a reusable skill.</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;Record a skill&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://infoq.cn/article/TWXI9ulbiPjRYmPFTGST' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>infoq.cn ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>In the official demo of the Record a skill feature, a 23.4-second recording was saved as a skill named /file-expenses.</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>{&quot;max&quot;: 23.4, &quot;min&quot;: 23.4}</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://infoq.cn/article/TWXI9ulbiPjRYmPFTGST' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>infoq.cn ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>The Record a skill in-product disclosure states that screen, clicks, keystrokes and voice will be recorded and sent for processing.</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;屏幕、点击、键入和语音会被记录并发送处理&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://infoq.cn/article/TWXI9ulbiPjRYmPFTGST' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>infoq.cn ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>部署的GPU为AMD Instinct MI450 Series</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;AMD Instinct MI450 Series&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://eenewseurope.com/en/amd-and-anthropic-partner-on-2gw-ai-gpu-deployment' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>eenewseurope.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>首批计划上线1GW容量</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;1&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://eenewseurope.com/en/amd-and-anthropic-partner-on-2gw-ai-gpu-deployment' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>eenewseurope.com ↗</a></p></section><section class='value-change'><h3>Anthropic将在AMD Helios机架级系统中部署最多2GW的AMD Instinct MI450系列GPU</h3><p><strong>变化方向：</strong>NEW_FACTOR · <strong>重要性：</strong>50</p><p><strong>原状态：</strong>此前未记录</p><p><strong>新状态：</strong><mark>&quot;2&quot;</mark></p><p><strong>证据：</strong><a href='https://eenewseurope.com/en/amd-and-anthropic-partner-on-2gw-ai-gpu-deplo